Log are very important feature.. Logs need to cleared always while checking code.. so change logs to local location

xd-admin log:
=======================

/opt/igc_services/igc_datastore_software/spring_xd/spring-xd-1.2.0.RELEASE/xd/config/xd-admin-logback.groovy

def logfileNameBase =/u/own/location/

property name:

Ex:

def logfileNameBase = "/opt/igc_services/runtime/spring_xd/logs/admin-${System.getProperty('PID')}"


xd-container Log:
===================

/opt/igc_services/igc_datastore_software/spring_xd/spring-xd-1.2.0.RELEASE/xd/config/xd-container-logback.groovy

property name:

def logfileNameBase = /ur/own/location/

Ex:

def logfileNameBase = "/opt/igc_services/runtime/spring_xd/logs/container-${System.getProperty('PID')}"

xd-singlenode-logback log:
==========================

/opt/igc_services/igc_datastore_software/spring_xd/spring-xd-1.2.0.RELEASE/xd/config/xd-singlenode-logback.groovy

def logfileNameBase = "/ur/own/location"

Ex:

def logfileNameBase = "/opt/igc_services/runtime/spring_xd/logs/singlenode-${System.getProperty('PID')}"

